OL,3,CMan whose body produces alcohol in
OL,4,Crare condition cleared of drunk driving
OL,6,FA Belgian man has been cleared of
OL,7,Fdrunk driving because he suffers from
OL,8,Fauto-brewery syndrome (ABS), a rare
OL,9,Fcondition where the body produces its
OL,10,Fown alcohol, his lawyer said.
OL,12,FHis lawyer, Anse Ghesquiere said that
OL,13,Fin "another unfortunate coincidence"
OL,14,Fher client works at a brewery, but
OL,15,Fthree doctors who independently
OL,16,Fexamined him confirmed he suffered
OL,17,Ffrom ABS.
