OL,3,CMan whose body produces alcohol in
OL,4,Crare condition cleared of drunk driving
OL,6,FLocal media said that in the verdict,
OL,7,Fthe judge emphasised that the
OL,8,Fdefendant, who was not named due to
OL,9,Flocal law custom, did not experience
OL,10,Fsymptoms of intoxication.
OL,12,FThe judge also refrained from issuing
OL,13,Fa driving ban due to his condition.
OL,15,FThose who have ABS can have symptoms
OL,16,Fsimilar to being drunk, including
OL,17,Fslurred speech, stumbling, loss of
OL,18,Fmotor functions, dizziness and
OL,19,Fbelching.
