OL,3,CMan whose body produces alcohol in
OL,4,Crare condition cleared of drunk driving
OL,6,FLisa Florin, clinical biologist with
OL,7,FBelgian hospital AZ Sint-Lucas,
OL,8,Fexplained that people with the
OL,9,Fcondition produce the same type of
OL,10,Falcohol as the one in alcoholic drinks
OL,11,Fbut that they generally feel less of
OL,12,Fits effects.
OL,14,FShe added that people are not born
OL,15,Fwith ABS but can get it when they
OL,16,Falready suffer from another intestine-
OL,17,Frelated condition.
